metadata.name: Perplexed
metadata.description: Brooklyn-based record label for emerging musical artists, toucan sounds presents a collection of NFTs made up of artwork by Dean Ruggieri, created for the EP and associated singles of Joey Mercedes' "Jump for Joy, Pause for Peace."   The NFTs were launched at a party celebrating the release at toucan sounds' music studio in Brooklyn, called YouTooCanWoo, on June 17, 2022.  The EP, "Jump for Joy, Pause for Peace," was released July 8, 2022. This is the artwork for the single, "Perplexed" by Joey Mercedes and Red Velvet Papi. Photos of Red Velvet Papi and Joey Mercedes appear on the artwork.
